        "body": "<p>I think you just need to use something like this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;LinearLayout android:orientation=\"vertical\"&gt;\n    &lt;ImageView android:src=\"@drawable/icon\" android:onClick=\"launchApp\" /&gt;\n    &lt;TextView android:text=\"@string/icon_name\" android:onClick=\"launchApp\" /&gt;\n&lt;/LinearLayout&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>and in your code you should have the corresponding method:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public void launchApp(View view) {\n // do something\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
